### GET forms

Resource URL: /forms

Headers:

* x-access-token = "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..O7YygxqCUBt8_86QiUjFyr2Dl2BozNInYEmTdNK4FTI"

Query Parameters:

* formId (optional)
* formCreatorId (optional. Filters forms by creator id)
* userId (optional. filters forms by userId)
* orderBy (optional), Possible values for orderBy (Prefix: F:Form, FS:Form section, FSF: Form section field and U:User)
                    are the following:
                        "name"
                        "dateCreated"
                        "creatorFullName"
* orderDirection (optional), valid values: "ASC", "DESC"                        
* pageSize (optional. Use with pageNumber to limit the amount of results)
* pageNumber (optional. Use with pageSize to paginate the results )
* justFormData (optional), valid values: "true", "false" (if added only the form data is sent without sections and fields)

* searchTerm (optional. Use to do a keyword search on formCreator and form name)
* searchByCreator (optional. Use to search by Form Creator user id)
* searchBySentTo (optional. Use to search by Sent to Subcontractor id)
* hiringClientId
